  m_text: "\n<size=10><b>What is Mixed Reality Toolkit?</b></size>\n\n<size=7>MRTK-Unity
    is a Microsoft-driven project that provides a set of components and features,
    used to accelerate cross-platform MR app development in Unity. \n\nMRTK3 is the
    third generation of Microsoft Mixed Reality Toolkit for Unity. This new version
    is built on top of Unity's XR Management system and XR Interaction Toolkit.</size>"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
